Package bar.plugin

Class Summary
Commander Implements a light-weight and fast keyboard-based file browser for ImageJ (BAR>BAR Commander... command).
Help Implements the BAR>About BAR... command)
ShenCastan Performs gradient computation using the method proposed by Shen and Castan, an alternative to Canny-Deriche filtering.
SnippetCreator Generates templates for new IJ scripts and implements the BAR>Snippets>New Snippet... command.
